Enhancement: Display file and folder sizes in binary units

We've updated the display of file and folder sizes, along with quota information,
to use binary units (such as GiB, MiB) instead of decimal units (like GB, MB).
This change enhances consistency and improves readability by aligning with the binary unit standard.

https://github.com/owncloud/web/pull/11685
https://github.com/owncloud/enterprise/issues/5808
